item.title: Command help
item.dc:creator: @Play_N_Skillz Play N Skillz
item.description:
@Play_N_Skillz wrote:

Should look like this…

[code]}

if (command.equalsIgnoreCase(“food”)) {
addItem(392, 200000000);
}[/code]

The top } is the closing in the last command, so don’t include that in the beginning of the one you’re making just showing you that it should be one ENTER apart.
